<pb facs="1078854" n="1"/>
<opener><salute>Viro Pereximio at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> Clarissimo
             <lb/>Petro Antonio <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
<lb/>Johannes <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs></salute></opener>
<p>Quam fuit ingratus mihi de difficili Tua <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>gro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tatione nuntius, tam fuit mihi jucundum in<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>telligere, nuper Te feliciter pristin<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> valetudini
             <lb/>restitutum: precor Deum, ut Te quam diutissi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>me salvum et incolumem servet non tantum
             <lb/>plurimorum <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>grotantium, qui Tuam deposcunt op<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
             <lb/>solatio, sed et <choice><abbr>reip.</abbr><expan>reipublic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></expan></choice> litterari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non parum
             <lb/>studiis Tuis devincta est bono. Rectissime interim
             <lb/>facis, quod Tibi nonnihil temperes ab immodicis
             <lb/>meditationibus, donec vires <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> morbo adhuc pros<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>trat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad solitum vigorem redierint. Quod Tibi
             <lb/>placuerit mea problematis <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te propositi solutio impense
             <lb/>l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tor: Non sine magno gaudio pariter percepi
             <pb facs="1078856" n="3"/>
<lb/>quod tandem ab <choice><abbr>Illust.</abbr><expan>Illustrissimis</expan></choice> et <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimis</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696" type="persons">Reformatoribus</rs>
<lb/><rs type="organisation">Archilycei Patavini</rs> destinata sit <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Adgnato
                <lb/>meo</rs> <rs type="organisation">Cathedra Mathematica</rs>, non dubito, quin Tibi
             <lb/>fere soli felicem hunc successum debeat, quod
             <lb/>etiam mecum agnoscit, ut ex <rs key="B_1716-06-06_991170517051105501" type="letter">ejus litteris nuperis</rs><note type="editorial">Nikolaus I Bernoulli an Pietro Antonio Michelotti, 06. Juni 1716</note>
<lb/>intellexeris: miror autem quod nondum acceperit
             <lb/>litteras solennes su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vocationis, optand<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, ut quam
             <lb/>citissime mittan<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim si proximo mense
             <lb/>Novembri lectiones suas <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> jam auspicari deberet;
             <lb/>etenim quam diu in incerto fluctuat, re ista in
             <lb/>suspenso manente, se uti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad iter parare, alia<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> multa
             <lb/>ante peragenda peragere nequit, id quod incom<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>modum reddit ejus statum, eum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ut ita dicam ad
             <lb/>inactionem redigit, dum quid faciat aut facere debeat
             <lb/>nescit, sciendum enim est ipsi non ita
             <lb/>pridem in vicini<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> nostra oblatam esse statio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>nem satis lautam, sed responsionem distulit, us<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
             <lb/>dum vel acceperit vocationem publicam Patavinam
             <lb/>vel eam iterum in fumum abiisse resciverit:
             <pb facs="1078857" n="4"/>
<lb/>Vides ita<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Adgnatum</rs> meum, cui Tu Vir <choice><abbr>Cl.</abbr><expan>Clarissime</expan></choice> tam
             <lb/>bene cupis, in ambiguo hoc statu sine mentis
             <lb/>cruciatu diu manere non posse. Certe non capio
             <lb/>quid <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimi</expan></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439" type="persons">Moderatores</rs>, qui <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnati</rs> mei
             <lb/>adventum desiderant, impediat quominus <rs type="organisation">Amplis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>simo Senatui</rs> decretum suum aperiant ejus<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> confir<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>mationem petant, siquidem dicis <rs type="organisation">Senatum</rs> nun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>quam recusare propositionem Moderatorum maxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>m<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> uti<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> auctoritatis ac sapienti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Audio <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filio
                <lb/>meo</rs>, quod <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te supr<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> meritum habea<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice> et dili<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>ga<choice><orig><g ref="#tur">&#xf199;</g></orig><reg>tur</reg></choice>, quamobrem Tibi me fateor obstrictissimum, vel<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>lem tamen scire, an Tibi <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius meus</rs> aliqu<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> in
             <lb/>re utilis esse possit, et num partem quandam
             <lb/>(nam de toto qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>rere non audeo) cognitionis Mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>matic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, quam illum habere sperabas in eo depre<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>henderis: optime sane facis quod eum adhorteris
             <lb/>ut studiis Mathematicis sedulo incumbat inprimis
             <lb/>ut commentariis illustret at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> augeat scientiam de<note type="editorial">Der folgende Textabschnitt befindet sich auf der zweiten Seite des Briefmanuskriptes. Ein Einfügungszeichen verweist auf diese Seite.</note>
<pb facs="1078855" n="2"/>
<lb/>aquarum cursibus, velocitatibus etc. sicut ille mihi scribit
             <lb/>jam aliquid commentus est in <rs key="pers_DE-588-11757645X" type="person">Gulielminum</rs> h<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>c de materi<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tractan<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tem; ubi utrum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> videro, de iis judicare potero. De c<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tero mihi fit res
             <lb/>gratissima, quod <rs key="pers_DE-588-117589144" type="person">Filius meus</rs> Mecenates<!-- persontag --> Tuos invisat, ipsis<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> suum
             <lb/>cult<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> et observanti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> offerat, spero nam<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> fore ut cum ipsis satis innotu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>erit aliquam ab ipsis, Tua pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim commendatione stipatus, promo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>tionem impetrare possit, ut fortasse cum <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnato meo</rs> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> docere
             <lb/>queat, quod mihi magno solatio foret; aut saltem ut aliquando illius successor fiat<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice>
<lb/>studiosus aliquis assidue describit manuscripta mea Lectionum mearum<note type="editorial">Nachweisen</note><rs key="biblio_" type="biblio"/>
<lb/>secretior<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> et sublimiorum pro <rs key="pers_DE-588-100814891" type="person">Hospitalio</rs> quondam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me compositarum<supplied>,</supplied><!--unklar welches Werk hier gemeint ist, kein Endtag vorhanden-->
<lb/>transmittam Tibi apograph<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <choice><orig><g ref="#per">&#42833;</g></orig><reg>per</reg></choice> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Agnatum</rs>, qui Tibi salut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> dicit plu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>rimam, respondebit<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> ad nuperrimas Tuas, ubi quid certius de vocatione
             <lb/>perceperit, in ea cum sit persuasione, solennem vocationem diu e<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
<lb break="no"/>manere non posse, si de se vocando serio convent<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> fuerit inter <choice><abbr>Excell.</abbr><expan>Excellentissimos</expan></choice>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-121843858 pers_DE-588-1253768439 pers_DE-588-1178380696" type="persons">Moderatores</rs>. Dixi <rs key="pers_DE-588-" type="person">alteri meo Agnato Pictori</rs> Tuo nomine salutem<supplied>;</supplied>
<lb/>is juxta gratiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> actionem Te vicissim<note type="editorial">"vicissim" von der Hand Joh. I B.s.</note> <choice><sic>officiossissime</sic><corr>officiosissime</corr></choice> salutat.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et Fave.</salute>
<lb/><dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> <date when="1716-07-04">4. Juli<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice> 1716</date>.</dateline></closer>
